- Version bump 1.3.0 → 1.4.0

### Why
This content was authored against v1.0.0 (the TQC citation PR) and is layered on top of main's v1.3.0
(Class A/B/C taxonomy + M55 Reality Offload). The Fibonacci vs. Ising/Majorana distinction is a non-obvious
trap (Microsoft Majorana 1 is not braiding-universal) and the TQC citations are reusable for any future
M-series mechanism in the topological/anyonic category. All prior v1.3.0/v1.2.0/v1.1.0/v1.0.0 content is
preserved below.

